index.html

Create this file at `/var/www/html/index.html` or in your local project folder first.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>AWS Cloud Web Hosting Project</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1> AWS Cloud Web Hosting Project</h1>
    <p>Hosted on Amazon EC2 (Linux) with Apache + PHP + SSL</p>
  </header>

  <section class="upload">
    <h2>Upload Your Files</h2>
    <form action="upload.php" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <input type="file" name="files[]" multiple required>
      <button type="submit">Upload</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>Created by <strong>Your Name</strong> | Cloud Developer</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

---

 upload.php

This script stores uploads in `/uploads/` with unique user folders.

```php
<?php
session_start();
if (!isset($_SESSION['user_id'])) {
    $_SESSION['user_id'] = uniqid('user_');
}
$user_id = $_SESSION['user_id'];
$dir = "uploads/" . $user_id . "/";
if (!file_exists($dir)) mkdir($dir, 0777, true);

foreach ($_FILES["files"]["name"] as $i => $name) {
    $target = $dir . basename($name);
    if (move_uploaded_file($_FILES["files"]["tmp_name"][$i], $target)) {
        echo "File $name uploaded successfully.<br>";
    } else {
        echo " Error uploading $name.<br>";
    }
}
echo "<br><a href='$dir'>View My Files</a> | <a href='index.html'>Back</a>";
?>
```

---

admin.php

Host-only dashboard showing all user uploads.

```php
<?php
$root = "uploads/";
echo "<h1> Admin Dashboard â€” All Uploaded Files</h1>";

if (is_dir($root)) {
    $users = scandir($root);
    foreach ($users as $u) {
        if ($u != "." && $u != "..") {
            echo "<h3>User: $u</h3><ul>";
            $files = scandir("$root/$u");
            foreach ($files as $f) {
                if ($f != "." && $f != "..") {
                    echo "<li><a href='$root/$u/$f' target='_blank'>$f</a></li>";
                }
            }
            echo "</ul>";
        }
    }
} else {
    echo "No uploads found.";
}
?>
```

