## Setup Commands
```bash
sudo yum update -y
sudo yum install httpd php -y
sudo systemctl enable httpd
sudo systemctl start httpd
sudo chmod -R 777 /var/www/html
````

## Add SSL

```bash
sudo yum install -y python3-certbot-apache
sudo certbot --apache
```

